ng about some "recovery amino acid complex" on the internet, I would've laughed at you.</p></span></div><div data-rid="2cc755b2-7f2f-4c76-8b3b-f9be16c2bbd8" class="r-dlp0ne alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>But here's the thing...</p></span></div><div data-rid="485a5646-dc38-4fad-a2d2-0df04f00420f" class="r-19i307v alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><strong>This shit's legit.</strong></p></span></div><div data-rid="931777f5-a20b-44e1-82ee-e36bb9878fe9" class="r-gazz4q alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>And if you told me six months ago that I'd be writing about some "recovery amino acid complex" on the internet, I would've laughed at you.</p></span></div><div data-rid="11ca383b-ceef-4e97-b5f0-bfc1039451ba" class="r-v50phn alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>Being distracted and unfocused is not something to shrug off. It can jeopardize people’s ability to hit their work targets and put them at risk of blowing their chances of a promotion. Even worse, it can mean losing out to coworkers who <span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong>can stay focused and get stuff done.</strong></span></p></span></div><div data-rid="aaae3f91-c6d8-4274-b9d9-8a37896d2ccf" class="r-1ny9kxh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0)"><strong>While some people waste hours scrolling endlessly through Instagram, others are finding ways to</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"> <strong>hack their brains to achieve optimal productivity,</strong></span> almost at will.</p></span></div></div><div data-rid="7273f3f1-df04-43dc-85f5-a57b33b86259" class="r-7yy0ik"><picture data-rid="1bce4221-b2d3-4b2c-9c23-6722d9171d1e" class="r-1pg7l8g"><img src="https://andytown-public.s3.us-west-1.amazonaws.com/templates/component-templates/Onnit-advert.json/63eb24ccca797b5c099f0c98_about15.jpg%3Fv%3D1678393304" class="r-77xkkg" loading="eager"/></picture><div data-rid="118feb50-c1d1-4326-a36d-ff5ec7125a5b" class="r-b4su3j"><div data-rid="a93c587c-b7ca-4673-af60-6cb539d8d89e" class="r-k0e3tu"></div><div data-rid="cd36b1ce-bafe-4e5c-b204-93dd37704c42" class="r-1sm00d3 alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>An Easier Way of Attaining Flow States</p></span></div><div data-rid="74038012-46dd-410f-b827-0d99637539e4" class="r-m9gm5r"></div></div><div data-rid="0bb451ab-e02a-4d81-9da6-588ad0995fb5" class="r-5ac3w7"><div data-rid="75b2719c-30a5-414b-8f26-07628b2dc60e" class="r-1vnl2xh alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>I'm not some guru trying to sell you on remarkable promotes wellness. I'm a 38-year-old former college wrestler who runs a construction company. I lift weights, I work with my hands, and my body takes a beating.</p></span></div><div data-rid="3419bc4b-0385-493b-8e30-51552defe718" class="r-irsnmd"><div class="r-3pxcqc"><video src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/dfad0de1-d0c4-4519-8bfa-03ad392ab394/0efbc86a-a7fa-475b-9b7e-f42da5cf13bb" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="metadata" autoplay="" muted="" loop=""></video></div><div data-rid="fc4e22ec-2f67-4e43-909c-546a88caf9a1" class="r-1eesyi"><div data-rid="a9b869c2-43da-457e-9ec3-c397e059036c" class="r-1vwakk4"><div data-rid="668f981e-3d51-4a7e-b547-7c95a734dfaf" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-1gjndlo"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" viewBox="0 0 16 16" role="presentation" aria-label="Pause" style="width:var(--rsw, 100%);height:auto;max-height:100%" class="r-136s9uw" height="1em" width="1em" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path d="M5.5 3.5A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 7 5v6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0V5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5m5 0A1.5 1.5 0 0 1 12 5v6a1.5 1.5 0 0 1-3 0V5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5-1.5"></path></svg></div></div><div data-rid="291b04a4-c700-4839-a953-a44366cb489a" class="r-u3iks0"><div data-rid="2b801752-24ad-446a-b169-c70151561c76" tabindex="0" role="button" class="r-15njm35"><svg stroke="currentColor" fill="currentColor" stroke-width="0" view