n style="width:100%"><p>But to <span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong>achieve a flow state</strong></span>, the brain needs to be at the right frequency. This frequency is when ‘alpha waves’ appear.</p></span></div><div data-rid="e4652c4c-c5f1-4ee3-857d-6fb04dd3819c" class="r-1qj4yet alchemy-rte"><span style="width:100%"><p>As reported in Psychology Today, neuroscientists have found alpha waves help to<span style="color: rgb(0, 119, 204)"><strong> support creativity and concentration.</strong></span> Until recently, the only way to trigger alpha waves was through sending electrical pulses through the brain or deep meditation.</p></span></div><div data-rid="399439c5-1d28-413c-8aaa-1eca035c6346" class="r-ilwo5v"><div data-rid="a7bc8b02-1539-4897-b59c-1abb2fba8ce0" class="r-r4dz9l"><div data-rid="8d26d2b3-aaee-4b4d-9a0b-252f86dc6541" class="r-1ovm7u0"><div class="r-1n1grne"><video src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/2b4cdd289f134a21b6736c80063f2c32.mp4" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="auto" autoplay="" muted="" loop=""></video></div><div data-rid="1004f712-a91f-4869-bb34-35ee9cd2ae38" class="r-1mz3q0n"></div></div></div><div data-rid="3dfc5052-ba07-4ab2-b005-c2a46a2e7160" class="r-1nb8970"><div data-rid="155adb9d-2eee-48b4-8f15-053e70dfb88f" class="r-2pctpo"><div class="r-1apv8pf"><video src="https://cdn.shopify.com/videos/c/o/v/797f8415c7474db2b34fcc37ce01bb25.mp4" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-position:var(--rop, inherit)" preload="metadata" muted=""></video></div><div data-rid="17f2e156-d40a-4563-a298-e23965c94ce6" class="r-1kn722f"></div></div></div></div><div data-rid="4e253e70-4169-4b6e-a35c-53083641f127" class="r-1pbhfjp"><div class="r-1vvr8ab"><video src="https://assets.replocdn.com/projects/dfad0de1-d0c4-4519-8bfa-03ad392ab394/fb49d8e2-9272-46c7-a7ad-46fad57cc42c" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:var(--rof, inherit);object-posit